Match
AUS vs IND ‚Ä¢ 3rd T20I ‚Ä¢ India tour of Australia, 2025
Series: India tour of Australia, 2025
Date: Today
Time: 7:15 PM LOCAL, 8:15 AM GMT

India have never played this format here. The bulk of the T20Is at this venue were played during the 2022 T20 World Cup. Australia have an unbeaten record here in five games having triumphed over Pakistan and once and twice each over West Indies and England. Hobart also has a bit of rolling out absolute batting beauties on occasions and when that happens the scores can get really high. Spinners didn't enjoy a great deal here last BBL but given the quality and variety of India's spinners Australia know they could still pose a challenge.
Welcome to Bellerive Oval, home to Hobart Hurricanes in the BBL - a place where Australia last year unearthed their latest white-ball bully in Mitchell Owen. He smashed two hundreds at this venue opening the batting to finish as the highest run scorer in his debut season. And he can bowl too. There are teams that struggle to produce all-rounders and there is Australia who not only get all-rounders but players who can make a strong impact with both bat and ball. Dinesh Vijan and Maddock Films present #Ikkis, a true untold story of India‚Äôs youngest Param Vir Chakra awardee - Second Lieutenant Arun Khetarpal directed by Sriram Raghavan.

snippet.title: Arasan - Official Trailer | Dhanush | Silambarasan TR | Vetri Maaran | Anirudh Ravichander
snippet.description:
Arasan - Official Trailer | Dhanush | Silambarasan TR | Vetri Maaran | Anirudh Ravichander 

This video is made only for showcasing the editing skills of the individual

Arasan is the title of Tamil star Silambarasan TR‚Äôs upcoming project with ace filmmaker Vetri Maaran, the makers announced on Tuesday (October 7). Produced by Kalaippuli S Thanu under his V Creations banner, the upcoming film is set in the world of Vetri‚Äôs acclaimed 2018 film Vada Chennai.

                    Other details, like the plot, remain unknown. While announcing the film in June, director Vetri Maaran revealed that the film, then tentatively called STR 49, is a parallel narrative set around the same time as Vada Chennai, and that ‚Äúcharacters and aspects from Vada Chennai will find their way into this story.
      
               A previously released promo video of the film showed a sickle-wielding Simbu, in a striped shirt and baggy pants, walking into a desolate lane. The video, however, cuts before his face is revealed. Interestingly, the title poster also intentionally hides the actor‚Äôs face, which certainly adds to the mystery.

While cast details have yet to be officially revealed, a leaked still from the set showed director Nelson alongside Simbu, prompting netizens to speculate that the director is playing a cameo in the film. Further speculations added that actors Kavin and Manikandan are also part of the film, and that actors Andrea Jeremiah, Samuthirakani and Kishore are reprising their roles from Vada Chennai. Vada Chennai, widely considered as one of the best gangster dramas in Tamil, featured Dhanush as a young man who is pulled into a world of crime, one where you either do or die. Over the years, the film has attained cult status among audiences. Interestingly, Vetri had also announced a spin-off series centred around Ameer Sultan‚Äôs character Rajan, titled Rajan Vagaiyara; however, there haven‚Äôt been any updates on the same.

With the voice of Silambarasan TR.

Worldwide Releasing On Oct 31st 2025.

CAST

id.title: Ulasan Pengungkapan Judul King | Shahrukh Khan | Siddharth Anand
id.description:
Ada kekosongan di tahun 2025 karena tidak ada film #SRK di tahun tersebut, tetapi inilah cuplikan pertama #King, proyek terbaru SRK bersama #Siddharthanand. Mungkinkah kombinasi ini akan memicu kehancuran yang sama seperti sebelumnya untuk menghidupkan kembali #Bollywood? Kita harus menunggu dan mencari tahu! Semoga Anda menyukai video yang membahas tentang pengungkapan judul dan beberapa elemennya. Video ini membahas:-

snippet.description:

Stream/Download:

(Lyrics):
[Verse 1: Zayn & Liam]
Goin' out tonight, changes into somethin' red
Her mother doesn't like that kind of dress
Everything she never had, she's showin' off
Drivin' too fast, moon is breakin' through her hair
She's headin' for somethin' that she won't forget
Havin' no regrets is all that she really wants

[Chorus: All & Harry]
(Ooh) We're only gettin' older, baby
(Ooh) And I've been thinkin' about it lately
(Ooh) Does it ever drive you crazy
(Ah-ah-ah) Just how fast the night changes?
(Ooh) Everything that you've ever dreamed of
(Ooh) Disappearin' when you wake up
(Ooh) But there's nothin' to be afraid of
(Ah-ah-ah) Even when the night changes
(Ooh) It will never change me and you

Chasin' her tonight, doubts are runnin' round her head
He's waitin', hides behind a cigarette
Heart is beatin' loud and she doesn't want it to stop
Movin' too fast, moon is lightin' up her skin
She's fallin', doesn't even know it yet
Havin' no regrets is all that she really wants

Ooh

Goin' out tonight, changes into somethin' red

Reminds her of the missin' piece of innocence she lost

snippet.description:
A heartfelt blend of timeless romance and modern soundscapes ‚Äî Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat Mera Hua brings together two beautiful worlds through emotion, melody, and passion.

Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat Mera Hua Mashup | Aftermorning | Harshvardhan | Shreya Ghoshal 
Remix  by : Aftermorning 
Mix Master: Vishal Rajput
Video Edit: Somnath Roy ( Afterlife Visual)
Release : AIDC
Music Production & Other work enquiries: yesugadeabhishek@gmail.com


Mera Hua
Shaam dhalti hai, aur main sochta hoon,
Tere bina bhi, main tujhmein kho jaata hoon.
Kuch lamhe the ‚Äî adhure, kuch sapne the ‚Äî pure,
Par har dafa tu tha, mere dil ke aas-paas zarur.
Yaad hai wo pal, jab tu muskurayi thi,
Waqt ruk gaya tha, khud zindagi sharmaayi thi.
Mujhe laga bas, ab kuch aur na chahiye,
Us ek pal ne, mujhe poora kar diya tha.
Tu door hai, par har subah tere saath uthta hoon,
Khidki se aane waali roshni mein tujhe dhoondhta hoon.
Tere bina bhi, tu mere saath hai,
Har saans mein tera ehsaas hai.
Kabhi socha nahi tha, pyaar itna chupke se aayega,
Zakhmon ko choo kar, dawa ban jaayega.
Tere jaane ke baad bhi, tu yahaan reh gaya,
Khali kamron mein, tera nasha mehka gaya.
Main likhta hoon, toh lafz tera roop le lete hain,
Gungunata hoon, toh sur tera naam keh dete hain.
Har silsilay ka anjaam tu ban gaya,
Main sirf tera tha‚Ä¶ aur tu mera hua.
Kahin duaon mein, kahin armaanon mein,
Tu likha gaya hai meri kahani ke har gumaanon mein.
Aur chahe duniya keh de ye pyaar bewajah,
Mujhe toh bas itna kehna hai ‚Äî
Tu mera sapna nahi‚Ä¶ mera sach hua.
Tu mera hua.
